This hallway is nearly identical to the previous one except the offices are bigger. The biggest one has a nameplate on the door, //Hunter Clarington//. He's the son of the CEO, you know, sent here to prove his worth to the company, or something like that.

There's another window at the end of this hallway. A red exit sign glows dimly, pointing to another stairwell further down the hall.
